title: Independent Candidate Ejaz Khan wins PS- 88 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent, Candidate Ejaz Khan has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-88, Malir-5 by securing 17,580 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Syed Muzamil Shah of PPPP’s, who bagged votes 12,762.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 37.88 %.
